title: Thyme Roasted Parsnip & Baby Rainbow Carrots with Honey Garlic Glaze | Serves 2
description: Get a good whiff of the herby aroma rising from this hearty side. The honey-garlic glaze reveals the delicate flavours hiding in the thyme and colourful roasted veggies while the toasted almonds never fail to add a satisfying crunch.
